Chaid<br>
51 (was 52) Rake on Drinal <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=emryss>emryss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/28/01 1:53:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pick Pocket Tips for Epic</span><hr size=1> I'm on my 11th Tani now. I've finally just given up after I've gotten all his coin followed by 20 unseccessful attempts. Sounds LIke I should give up after 10 failures instead. Last time I got coin or loot from him 6 times in a row, then failed 20 times in a row, then gave up.  I always wondered at what point I should give up on a particular spawn, but as long as the note is no different to the game as his other loot, it seems like 10 failures is a good sign he doesn't have it heh. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umaslethalo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>maslethalo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/28/01 2:17:00 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pick Pocket Tips for Epic</span><hr size=1> do it with a cleric, if you die and the cleric is KoS just leave a corpse at zone line.  Get rez'd in drag other corpse back and get exp rez.<br>
<br>
I would pick more than 10 times, I got note after 10 attempts on 2nd spawn. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uetaudarg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Etaudarg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/28/01 3:57:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pick Pocket Tips for Epic</span><hr size=1> Did Tani with no problems, got my note on about the 6th visit. I have yet to get the note of Founy.. been 3 days in RL prolly tried it more than 20times, got cought several times relatively easy to run to the exit (guy hits for a max of 150dmg not sure what the backstabs are).<br>
<br>
So basically im finding getting the note of Founy is abit harder..<br>
<br>
cheers <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
good luck to all on your epics.. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uetaudarg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Etaudarg</A> at: 11/28/01 5:17:53 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uteramenor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teramenor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/28/01 6:48:00 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pick Pocket Tips for Epic</span><hr size=1> All of the Guides and GMs I've asked (about 10 guides and 4 GMs) do seem to think that pickpocketing Tani from the roof is an exploit. I wouldn't recommend it.<br>
