I would pick more than 10 times, I got note after 10 attempts on 2nd spawn. &quot;<br>
<br>
I think the hard part is getting the KoS cleric TO 3rd gate, since you gotta go thru 2 other DE zones to get there, and past bottlenecks where you MUST pass within aggro range of a DE guard or 3.<br>
